📚 Recommended Free Books

Open Data Structures (In C++) – Pat Morin
A fully open‐access textbook that covers many data structures, analyses, and implementations in C++. The author even treats the book “like an open source software project”. 
link: https://opendatastructures.org/ods-cpp.pdf

Data Structures and Algorithm Analysis in C++ (3rd Edition) – Clifford A. Shaffer
A textbook focused on algorithm analysis and data structures using C++. 
link: https://digitalcommons.liberty.edu/textbooks/6/

Data Structures and Algorithms in C++ – Michael T. Goodrich, Roberto Tamassia, David M. Mount
Another solid choice with object-oriented design plus algorithms and data structures in C++. 
link: https://www.wiley-vch.de/en/areas-interest/computing-computer-sciences/data-structures-and-algorithms-in-c-978-0-470-38327-8


